<section class="pb0">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-12 text-center">
        <h4 class="uppercase">About Antlers</h4>
        <p>
          Antlers is a full service creative agency located in Bandung. What we are about is handling and providing creative communication design services for our clients. Our priority is making the best work with the purposes of client needs. Antlers help you to develop your strategy, define its character and deliver the message properly. We also have a suitable offering for your business and budget.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <%- @teams.each do |team| %>
        <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">
          <div class="image-tile outer-title text-center">
            <%= image_tag team.photo_url(:team_photo).nil? ? 'team.jpg' : team.photo_url(:team_photo), :alt => 'Growantlers - ' + team.name %>
